17:21.174 --> 17:22.242
[thud]

17:22.275 --> 17:24.144
- I DIDN'T MEAN LITERALLY.

17:24.177 --> 17:27.214
- I WISH YOU'D DROP IT TOO.
THIS CHARMING MOOD.

17:27.247 --> 17:28.815
- I CAN'T HELP IT.

17:28.848 --> 17:31.451
OH, I SHOULD NEVER
HAVE ASKED THEM.

17:31.484 --> 17:35.455
- SO YOU DID.
THEY SAID NO. NOW IT'S OVER.

17:35.488 --> 17:38.125
COME ON. LET'S GO LOOK
AT WEDDING CAKES.

17:38.158 --> 17:40.293
- WHAT FOR?
WE CAN'T AFFORD ONE.

17:40.327 --> 17:41.661
