- LOVE?

17:53.540 --> 17:55.442
YOU WANT THEM TO SHOW YOU
THE SAME ATTENTION

17:55.475 --> 17:58.411
THEY SHOW LYNNETTE.

17:58.445 --> 18:00.347
- YEAH.

18:00.380 --> 18:03.783
- MAYBE WE HAVE TO PUT FORTH
MORE OF AN EFFORT.

18:03.816 --> 18:05.518
