JUST AS GUILTY AS THEY ARE.

18:15.195 --> 18:17.464
- SO WHAT DO WE DO?

18:17.497 --> 18:20.367
- INVITE THEM OVER.
THROW A LITTLE PARTY.

18:20.400 --> 18:22.902
- YOU'RE SERIOUS.

18:22.935 --> 18:26.539
- IF THEY COULD SEE
THAT WE'RE A REAL FAMILY

18:26.573 --> 18:29.376
