JUST LIKE YOUR SISTER,

18:29.409 --> 18:33.180
THEY MIGHT FEEL DIFFERENTLY.

18:33.213 --> 18:37.717
HEY, IT'S AT LEAST
WORTH A SHOT.

18:37.750 --> 18:40.653
COME ON.

18:46.893 --> 18:48.395
- MAY I SHOW YOU SOMETHING?

18:48.428 --> 18:50.163
- YEAH. WE'D LIKE
TO LOOK AT WEDDING CAKES.

18:50.197 --> 18:51.864
- OH, LOVELY.
THEY'RE OUR SPECIALTY.

