19:25.532 --> 19:27.934
AND IF YOU HAVE
JUST ONE LITTLE FUCK-UP,

19:27.967 --> 19:30.670
ONE MOMENT OF FORGETFULNESS,
JUST ONE MISTAKE,

19:30.703 --> 19:34.507
IT COULD KILL YOU TOO.

19:34.541 --> 19:36.676
- I THINK YOU'RE BEING
A LITTLE DRAMATIC, TEDDY.

19:36.709 --> 19:37.977
- [scoffs]

19:38.010 --> 19:39.212
- THERE ARE PLENTY
OF GUYS WHO HAVE BOYFRIENDS

19:39.246 --> 19:40.280
WHO ARE POSITIVE.

19:40.313 --> 19:42.482
- WELL, THOSE PEOPLE
AREN'T MICHAEL.

19:42.515 --> 19:43.716
AND YOU WEREN'T
SO FUCKING NONCHALANT

19:43.750 --> 19:45.418
WHEN YOU THOUGHT
YOU MIGHT HAVE BEEN INFECTED.

19:45.452 --> 19:47.287
- LOOK, I APPRECIATE
YOUR CONCERN,

19:47.320 --> 19:49.489
