LIKE HE'S A DISEASE

19:49.522 --> 19:52.459
AND NOT A PERSON.

19:52.492 --> 19:54.327
AND IF YOU WERE SEEING
SOMEONE THAT YOU CARED ABOUT

19:54.361 --> 19:56.763
WHO WAS POSITIVE,
I THINK YOU'D FEEL DIFFERENTLY.

19:56.796 --> 19:58.798
- NO, I'M SORRY, I KNOW
IT'S NOT POLITICALLY CORRECT

19:58.831 --> 20:00.633
