21:05.865 --> 21:10.837
- OH, UM, PREPARING A LIST.

21:10.870 --> 21:13.840
- WELL, YOU CAN DO YOUR
GROCERY SHOPPING LATER, OKAY?

21:13.873 --> 21:16.843
- IT'S--UH, IT'S NOT
THAT KIND OF LIST.

21:16.876 --> 21:19.446
