FOR A LONG SHOT.

22:03.523 --> 22:07.427
- WELL, EXCUSE ME, CHER,
BUT THERE'S ONLY ONE LONG SHOT

22:07.460 --> 22:09.429
YOUR FANS ARE INTERESTED IN,
SO COME ON.

22:09.462 --> 22:11.664
[snaps fingers]
LESS YAK AND MORE JACK.

22:11.698 --> 22:16.636
- WHAT ABOUT MY DEMANDS?
- [scoffs] WHAT, YOU MEAN THESE?

22:18.605 --> 22:23.843
LOOK, EMMETT,

22:23.876 --> 22:25.712
IF IT WEREN'T FOR ME,

22:25.745 --> 22:28.047
