AS A NAKED MAID,

22:28.080 --> 22:29.416
"BUFFING IN THE BUFF,"

22:29.449 --> 22:30.950
TRYING TO PICK UP
A FEW EXTRA BUCKS, OKAY?

22:30.983 --> 22:33.586
- YEAH, AND, UH,
AND IF IT WEREN'T FOR ME,

22:33.620 --> 22:36.923
