PULLING YOUR PUD.

22:36.956 --> 22:38.758
- OH, SO I OWE
ALL THIS TO YOU?

22:38.791 --> 22:41.861
- HMM. DIFFICULT QUESTION.
LET ME THINK.

22:41.894 --> 22:44.063
YES!

22:44.096 --> 22:46.866
- I CAN REPLACE YOU
WHENEVER I WANT.

22:46.899 --> 22:49.469
THEN WE'LL SEE HOW QUICKLY
YOUR FANS FORGET.

22:49.502 --> 22:50.837
- REALLY?
- REALLY.

22:50.870 --> 22:53.506
DICKS LIKE YOU...

22:53.540 --> 22:56.643
DIME A DOZEN.

22:58.478 --> 22:59.812
- WELL, I TELL YOU WHAT.

22:59.846 --> 23:03.015
YOU FIND SOME TWINKY
WITH A DINKY,

23:03.049 --> 23:05.117
AND SEE HOW
FAR YOU GET.

23:05.151 --> 23:09.021
OH, AND WHEN YOU DO,
GIVE HIM THIS.

23:09.055 --> 23:11.991
HE'S GOING TO NEED IT.

23:17.530 --> 23:19.466
- LAST TIME I SAW YOU
CLEANING THE TCHOTCKES

23:19.499 --> 23:22.835
WAS WHEN MICHAEL
MOVED AWAY WITH DAVID.

23:22.869 --> 23:26.038
- I'M JUST SICK OF SEEING THIS
PLACE LIKE A GODDAMNED PIGSTY.

23:26.072 --> 23:30.477
THAT'S ALL.

23:30.510 --> 23:32.579
- WOULD YOU STOP WINDEXING
FOR HALF A SECOND

23:32.612 --> 23:35.648
AND TALK TO ME?

23:35.682 --> 23:41.187
- I CAN'T.
- WHY NOT?

23:41.220 --> 23:45.725
- IT'S PERSONAL.

23:45.758 --> 23:48.761
- WHAT COULD BE PERSONAL
AFTER YOU'VE WIPED MY ASS?

23:48.795 --> 23:52.565
