24:33.773 --> 24:37.544
THAT MICHAEL'S DATING,
THIS, UM, THIS BEN.

24:41.648 --> 24:44.050
HE'S POSITIVE.

24:44.083 --> 24:46.719
- OH.

24:46.753 --> 24:49.088
SO?

24:49.121 --> 24:53.125
- SO...

24:53.159 --> 24:55.995
