DATING ANYONE WHO'S SICK.

24:56.028 --> 24:58.831
- WHO SAID HE'S SICK?

25:01.233 --> 25:04.537
- I KNEW I COULDN'T
TALK TO YOU ABOUT IT.

25:04.571 --> 25:05.972
- SO NEGATIVE PEOPLE
SHOULDN'T BE ALLOWED

25:06.005 --> 25:07.707
TO DATE POSITIVE PEOPLE,
IS THAT IT?

25:07.740 --> 25:10.777
- DON'T TWIST MY WORDS!

25:13.245 --> 25:15.748
- THEN WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

25:15.782 --> 25:17.884
- HE'S MY SON.

25:17.917 --> 25:20.987
I DON'T WANT HIM
GETTIN' ANYTHING.

25:27.694 --> 25:31.197
