IN MY LIFE,

25:33.065 --> 25:34.834
I WISH MY SON WASN'T GAY.

25:34.867 --> 25:37.704
- YOU DON'T MEAN THAT.

25:37.737 --> 25:40.773
- NOT IF IT MEANS
I HAVE TO WATCH HIM PUKING,

25:40.807 --> 25:44.611
AND SHITTING
AND WASTING AWAY TO NOTHING.

25:44.644 --> 25:46.846
- I CAN'T LISTEN
TO ANY MORE OF THIS.

25:46.879 --> 25:50.016
- DO YOU THINK I WANT MICHAEL
TO END UP LIKE YOU?

25:53.753 --> 25:56.956
