25:56.989 --> 26:00.593
OH, SHIT. MICHAEL!

26:03.730 --> 26:05.698
I'M JUST GETTING SOME STUFF
AND THEN I'M OUT OF HERE.

26:05.732 --> 26:07.166
- HONEY...

26:07.199 --> 26:08.668
LOOK, MICHAEL, SWEETHEART--

26:08.701 --> 26:10.002
- HOW COULD YOU TALK THAT WAY
TO UNCLE VIC?

26:10.036 --> 26:11.070
YOU REALLY HURT HIM!

26:11.103 --> 26:14.206
- PEOPLE SAY A LOT OF THINGS
WHEN THEY'RE UPSET.

26:14.240 --> 26:18.344
AND I'M UPSET.
I'M VERY FUCKING UPSET.

26:18.377 --> 26:20.212
AND HOW LONG
WERE YOU GONNA WAIT

26:20.246 --> 26:23.115
BEFORE YOU TOLD ME
ABOUT BEN?

26:23.149 --> 26:24.984
- I DIDN'T THINK YOU'D CARE!

26:25.017 --> 26:26.853
ESPECIALLY AFTER
ALL THE NOBLE SENTIMENTS

26:26.886 --> 26:31.257
AND HASH BROWNS YOU WERE
DISHING OUT AT THE DINER.

26:31.290 --> 26:33.192
- ALL RIGHT.

26:33.225 --> 26:37.329
I'M GONNA MAKE YOU VERY,
VERY HAPPY.

26:37.363 --> 26:40.667
YOU ALWAYS WANTED
A NORMAL MOTHER?

26:40.700 --> 26:43.703
OKAY, YOU GOT ONE.

26:43.736 --> 26:45.271
I DON'T WANT YOU
DATING THAT GUY.

26:45.304 --> 26:49.175
- I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU WANT!
AND DON'T TELL ME WHO TO DATE!

26:49.208 --> 26:50.777
I'M 30 YEARS OLD.

26:50.810 --> 26:52.979
WHO I DATE
AND WHAT I DO

26:53.012 --> 26:56.215
IS NONE OF YOUR GODDAMN
FUCKING BUSINESS!

27:03.389 --> 27:05.958
- WE'RE REALLY LUCKY.

27:05.992 --> 27:08.027
- WHAT? LIVING IN
THIS LAND OF PLENTY?

27:08.060 --> 27:10.663
HMM. ROLL OVER.

27:14.734 --> 27:16.836
- EVERY TIME MICHAEL
AND BEN HAVE SEX,

27:16.869 --> 27:19.271
THINK OF ALL THAT
THEY HAVE TO DEAL WITH.

27:19.305 --> 27:23.075
- IT'S MICHAEL'S DECISION.

27:23.109 --> 27:25.444
IS THAT A PIMPLE
ON YOUR ASS?

27:25.477 --> 27:27.146
- WHERE?
- RIGHT THERE.

27:27.179 --> 27:28.380
- WHERE?
- RIGHT THERE.

27:28.414 --> 27:31.417
- SHUT UP.

27:34.854 --> 27:37.023
NO MATTER HOW LONG
THEY'RE TOGETHER,

27:37.056 --> 27:41.327
EVEN IF IT'S FOREVER,
THEY CAN NEVER DO IT RAW.

27:41.360 --> 27:44.697
- UM, NEITHER HAVE WE.

27:44.731 --> 27:49.401
- YEAH, BUT WE COULD.
IF WE WANTED.

27:52.104 --> 27:54.841
I MEAN...

27:54.874 --> 27:57.877
WE'RE BOTH NEGATIVE.

28:00.847 --> 28:04.316
- YOU WANT ME
TO FUCK YOU BAREBACK?

28:04.350 --> 28:06.719
- YES.

28:06.753 --> 28:08.921
- COME INSIDE
YOUR TIGHT LITTLE ASS?

28:08.955 --> 28:13.392
- DO IT.

28:13.425 --> 28:17.296
FUCK ME.

28:17.329 --> 28:23.169
- FUCK YOURSELF.
- WHAT?

28:23.202 --> 28:26.338
- YOU STUPID LITTLE TWAT.

28:26.372 --> 28:29.809
NEVER LET ANYONE
FUCK YOU WITHOUT A CONDOM.

28:29.842 --> 28:31.210
- YOU'RE NOT JUST ANYONE.

28:31.243 --> 28:33.145
- YEAH, I'M SURE THAT'S
WHAT BEN THOUGHT ABOUT THE GUY

28:33.179 --> 28:37.316
WHO INFECTED HIM.

28:41.387 --> 28:44.957
PUT IT ON ME.

28:51.163 --> 28:54.166
HMM.

29:01.207 --> 29:03.976
MM!

29:07.413 --> 29:11.750
- [gasping]

29:15.054 --> 29:18.991
- I WANT YOU SAFE.

29:19.025 --> 29:21.127
AND I WANT YOU AROUND
FOR A LONG TIME.

29:21.160 --> 29:24.763
- [sighs]

29:27.900 --> 29:29.235
- WOULD YOU ASK LINDSAY

29:29.268 --> 29:31.303
WHERE SHE WANTS ME
TO PUT THESE PLATES?

29:31.337 --> 29:32.905
- THE BLUE OR THE RED?

29:32.939 --> 29:35.574
- OKAY. THE TEA SERVICE
IS POLISHED.

29:35.607 --> 29:37.276
THE FLOWERS ARE ALL ARRANGED.

29:37.309 --> 29:40.546
THOSE VEGETARIAN ROLL-UPS
LOOK SCRUMPTIOUS. HUH.

29:40.579 --> 29:43.549
HOW DO I LOOK?

29:43.582 --> 29:46.285
- LIKE A FUCKING NUN.
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR TITS?

29:48.287 --> 29:49.889
- [sighs]

29:49.922 --> 29:51.390
- WHO KNEW MY YEAR WORKING
IN A PIERCING SALON

29:51.423 --> 29:53.259
WOULD COME IN SO HANDY.

29:53.292 --> 29:55.427
[doorbell rings]
- THAT'S TASHA AND HER HARP.

29:55.461 --> 29:57.029
- SOMEBODY BETTER GET THE DOOR.

29:57.063 --> 29:59.165
- I JUST PUT IT DOWN.
DID YOU GRAB IT?

29:59.198 --> 30:00.900
- OH, SORRY.

30:00.933 --> 30:02.434
- I WAS HOPING
YOU WERE THE HARP.

30:02.468 --> 30:05.371
- [scoffs] I'M INTO
FUCKING NOT PLUCKING.

30:05.404 --> 30:07.907
WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR TITS?

30:07.940 --> 30:11.177
HEY, SONNY-BOY, YOUR OLD MAN'S
HERE TO RESCUE YOU.

30:11.210 --> 30:14.914
- HI, I'M LEDA.

30:14.947 --> 30:17.984
- AH, MELANIE'S EVIL EX.

30:18.017 --> 30:20.419
- AND YOU MUST
BE THE ANTICHRIST.

30:20.452 --> 30:22.922
BIG FAN.

30:22.955 --> 30:24.456
OH, DON'T BOTHER,
IT'S A VIRGIN.

30:24.490 --> 30:27.059
- THE SITTER'S COMING
FOR GUS THIS AFTERNOON.

30:27.093 --> 30:28.594
TAKE HIM TO THE PARK.

30:28.627 --> 30:30.529
BE CAREFUL ON THE SWINGS.
DON'T GET HIM DIRTY.

30:30.562 --> 30:34.300
BE BACK BY 2:00.
AND WEAR SOMETHING NICE.

30:34.333 --> 30:36.235
- ANYTHING ELSE?
- SHAVE.

30:36.268 --> 30:40.339
- MY BALLS ARE AS CLEAN
AS A WHISTLE.

30:40.372 --> 30:41.340
[phone rings]

30:41.373 --> 30:43.209
- HI.
- TASHA, FINALLY.

30:43.242 --> 30:44.877
LEDA, CAN YOU
SHOW HER WHERE TO PUT IT?

30:44.911 --> 30:48.314
- [chuckles]
- IT'S TOO EASY.

30:48.347 --> 30:50.482
- WE'RE TRYING TO MAKE
LINDSAY'S PARENTS FEEL AT HOME.

30:50.516 --> 30:52.251
- WELL, YOU SHOULD
HAVE RENTED CASKETS.

30:52.284 --> 30:54.921
- I SAY WE GREET 'EM
WEARING STRAP-ONS.

30:54.954 --> 30:57.256
EVER BEEN FUCKED
BY A DYKE WITH A DILDO?

30:57.289 --> 30:58.925
- [chuckles]
IS THAT AN OFFER?

30:58.958 --> 31:00.492
- THIS IS REALLY
IMPORTANT TO LINDSAY,

31:00.526 --> 31:04.396
SO COULD BOTH OF YOU KEEP
YOUR FUCKING FOUL MOUTHS SHUT?

31:10.236 --> 31:13.405
- THEY'RE NOT COMING.

31:15.007 --> 31:17.343
- ARE WE SURPRISED?

31:17.376 --> 31:18.978
- MOM SAID DADDY
SLIPPED A DISC

31:19.011 --> 31:21.180
AND HE'LL BE ON HIS BACK
FOR DAYS.

31:21.213 --> 31:23.115
- WELL,
THAT I'D LIKE TO SEE.

31:23.149 --> 31:26.485
- SHUT UP, BRIAN.
- [giggles]

31:26.518 --> 31:29.621
[door closes]

31:33.192 --> 31:35.928
- IT WAS LIKE AN EPISODE
OF THE TWILIGHT ZONE.

31:35.962 --> 31:37.163
- MY FAVORITE WAS THE ONE
WHERE YOU COULD

31:37.196 --> 31:40.332
TRADE IN YOUR OLD BODY
FOR A HOT, NEW ONE.

31:40.366 --> 31:45.071
- SHE ACTUALLY SAID
SHE WISHED I WASN'T GAY.

31:45.104 --> 31:48.907
- WELL, I'LL ALWAYS BE GLAD
YOU'RE A BIG, FAT QUEER.

31:52.278 --> 31:55.414
- YOU TWO MAKE
A BEAUTIFUL COUPLE.

31:55.447 --> 31:59.185
HEY, THERE, AREN'T YOU SWEET?

31:59.218 --> 32:02.121
HI, SWEETIE.

32:02.154 --> 32:04.290
AND YOUR BABY LOOKS
JUST LIKE YOU.

32:04.323 --> 32:07.726
[chuckles]

32:07.759 --> 32:09.661
- [mock chuckle]
- [laughs]

32:09.695 --> 32:13.099
- SO SWEET.

32:13.132 --> 32:15.167
YOU KNOW, SHE'S RIGHT.

32:15.201 --> 32:16.302
- WHAT ARE
YOU TALKING ABOUT?

32:16.335 --> 32:17.436
THE BABY'S THE SPITTING IMAGE
OF YOU.

32:17.469 --> 32:20.706
- I MEAN DEBBIE.

32:20.739 --> 32:22.274
YOU SHOULD FORGET BEN.

32:22.308 --> 32:25.411
- [sighs] WHAT
THE FUCK DO YOU KNOW?

32:25.444 --> 32:28.514
- WELL, LET'S SEE,
I KNOW ADVERTISING.

32:28.547 --> 32:30.449
AND I KNOW YOU.

32:30.482 --> 32:32.184
THOSE ADS YOU SEE
FOR THE COCKTAILS

32:32.218 --> 32:35.587
WITH THE GREAT-LOOKING GUYS
SKIING AND MOUNTAIN-CLIMBING,

32:35.621 --> 32:36.722
LIKE ALL YOU
HAVE TO DO

32:36.755 --> 32:38.290
IS POP A LITTLE
PROTEASE INHIBITOR,

32:38.324 --> 32:42.461
AND YOU TOO CAN HAVE
THE TIME OF YOUR LIFE.

32:42.494 --> 32:45.064
WELL, IT'S JUST KIND
OF TOUGH DOWNHILL RACING

32:45.097 --> 32:48.067
WHEN YOU'VE GOT
NON-STOP DIARRHEA.

32:48.100 --> 32:52.738
- I CAN HANDLE IT.
- WELL, THEN HANDLE IT.

32:52.771 --> 32:58.177
KISS IT. JERK IT OFF.
JUST DON'T FALL IN LOVE WITH IT.

33:02.214 --> 33:06.485
- MRS. PETERSEN?
- MELANIE. WHAT A SURPRISE.

33:11.657 --> 33:13.659
UNFORTUNATELY,
I'M JUST ON MY WAY OUT.

33:13.692 --> 33:16.762
- GEORGE, BARBARA,
IS THAT YOU?

33:16.795 --> 33:20.499
- MR. PETERSEN.

33:20.532 --> 33:23.702
- I WAS EXPECTING--
- SOMEONE ELSE?

33:23.735 --> 33:26.505
CONGRATULATIONS
ON YOUR SPEEDY RECOVERY.

33:26.538 --> 33:28.640
- WELL, YOU KNOW HOW
IT IS WITH THESE BACK THINGS.

33:28.674 --> 33:30.642
ONE MINUTE YOU CAN'T STAND UP,
THE NEXT MINUTE--

33:30.676 --> 33:33.612
- PLAYING MIXED DOUBLES.

33:34.813 --> 33:37.283
- THIS IS VERY AWKWARD.
[clears throat]

33:37.316 --> 33:39.785
- AWKWARD? THAT YOU COULDN'T
COME OVER TO OUR HOUSE

33:39.818 --> 33:42.121
FOR A COUPLE OF HOURS?

33:42.154 --> 33:44.356
LINDSAY'S BEEN WORKING
HER ASS OFF FOR YOU.

33:44.390 --> 33:46.192
WOULD IT BE SO FUCKING HARD
TO SHOW UP?

33:46.225 --> 33:49.495
- LANGUAGE.
- LANGUAGE.

33:49.528 --> 33:52.364
- YOUR EXCUSES ARE BULLSHIT.

33:52.398 --> 33:54.133
ALL SHE WANTS FROM YOU

33:54.166 --> 33:55.801
IS TO SHOW HER
A LITTLE SUPPORT.

33:55.834 --> 33:58.070
- THE ONLY REASON YOU WANT US
TO COME TO YOUR PARTY

33:58.104 --> 34:00.172
IS SO THAT WE'LL
WRITE YOU A CHECK.

34:00.206 --> 34:02.541
- NANCY, PLEASE.
- WHY NOT ADMIT IT?

34:02.574 --> 34:06.278
- LOOK, I KNOW WHAT
YOU THINK ABOUT ME.

34:06.312 --> 34:08.380
I'M THE SLICK JEW LAWYER
COME TO SHAKE YOU DOWN

34:08.414 --> 34:11.150
FOR A FEW SHEKELS.

34:11.183 --> 34:13.452
THE DYKE WHO CORRUPTED
YOUR DAUGHTER.

34:13.485 --> 34:15.154
WELL, YOU'RE WRONG.

34:15.187 --> 34:20.359
I'M LINDSAY'S LOVING PARTNER
AND GUS'S ADORING MOTHER.

34:20.392 --> 34:23.362
AND I KNOW THAT I WILL
NEVER CAUSE HIM THE PAIN

34:23.395 --> 34:25.397
THAT YOU'VE CAUSED HER.

34:25.431 --> 34:28.734
HE'LL NEVER HAVE TO WONDER
WHETHER OR NOT I LOVE HIM.

35:02.701 --> 35:04.403
- ARE WE GONNA TALK?

35:04.436 --> 35:08.874
OR ARE WE JUST GONNA RAKE
THE WHOLE GODDAMN NEIGHBORHOOD?

35:08.907 --> 35:12.744
- IF YOU WANT
TO TALK, TALK.

35:12.778 --> 35:16.148
- YOU KNOW I DIDN'T
MEAN WHAT I SAID.

35:16.182 --> 35:19.718
WELL, FOR IT TO COME OUT
THE WAY IT DID.

35:21.787 --> 35:25.624
I'VE JUST HAD IT
WITH THIS FUCKING DISEASE.

35:25.657 --> 35:28.794
- TELL ME ABOUT IT.

35:28.827 --> 35:31.563
- I KNOW, BABY.

35:35.934 --> 35:38.670
I JUST CAN'T
GO THROUGH IT AGAIN.

35:40.906 --> 35:43.509
- WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
YOU'LL HAVE TO?

35:43.542 --> 35:46.645
MICHAEL DOESN'T HAVE HIV.
- BEN DOES.

35:46.678 --> 35:48.247
AND THERE'S NOTHING
IN HIS LIFE

35:48.280 --> 35:49.648
THAT'S NOT GONNA
BE AFFECTED BY IT,

35:49.681 --> 35:52.251
INCLUDING MICHAEL.

35:52.284 --> 35:56.622
AND WHAT AFFECTS MICHAEL,
AFFECTS ME.

35:56.655 --> 35:58.924
- IT'S LIKE WHAT THEY SAY
ABOUT MARRIAGE.

35:58.957 --> 36:01.827
YOU DON'T JUST GET THEM,
YOU GET THE WHOLE DAMN FAMILY.

36:01.860 --> 36:05.564
- YEAH, WELL, I'M NOT SO CRAZY
ABOUT THE IN-LAWS.

36:06.865 --> 36:09.468
- [chuckles]

36:15.974 --> 36:19.845
- I MEAN, EVEN
IF THEY HAVE SAFE SEX,

36:19.878 --> 36:22.981
WHAT IF SOMETHING HAPPENS?

36:23.014 --> 36:26.685
WHAT IF MICHAEL COMES TO US
AND HE SAYS, "I'VE GOT IT?"

36:30.289 --> 36:32.491
WHAT DO WE DO?

36:35.794 --> 36:38.864
- FIRST WE'D DIE.

36:41.800 --> 36:45.904
AND THEN WE'D DEAL WITH IT.

36:59.885 --> 37:01.720
[chuckles]

37:03.722 --> 37:05.724
- [clears throat]

37:05.757 --> 37:07.926
- THIS PARTY SUCKS.

37:07.959 --> 37:12.331
- I PREFER TO THINK
OF IT AS MELLOW.

37:12.364 --> 37:15.734
- I'M GOING TO GO UPSTAIRS
AND SWALLOW A BOTTLE OF XANAX.

37:15.767 --> 37:19.271
- GOOD IDEA.

37:19.305 --> 37:21.873
- FUCKING FLOWERS ARE MAKING
MY ALLERGIES GO BERSERK.

37:21.907 --> 37:25.344
- OH! WHOOPEE, THAT'S
A GOOD REASON TO LEAVE.

37:25.377 --> 37:27.746
- AND LEAVE ME ALONE
WITH THE LADIES WHO MUNCH?

37:27.779 --> 37:29.681
NO WAY.

37:29.715 --> 37:32.818
- UH, WELL, IN THAT CASE,
I GUESS THERE'S ONLY ONE THING

37:32.851 --> 37:36.021
WE CAN DO.

37:36.054 --> 37:38.790
- YAY!
- [chuckles]

37:41.427 --> 37:43.695
- YOU KNOW, I CAN HONESTLY
SAY THERE IS, UH,

37:43.729 --> 37:46.398
THERE'S NOT ONE THING HERE
I'D PUT IN MY MOUTH.

37:46.432 --> 37:49.501
- THAT'S A FIRST.

37:49.535 --> 37:51.403
- EXCUSE ME?

37:51.437 --> 37:54.039
- THIS FOOD'S THE WORST.

37:57.809 --> 38:00.512
- OH, DID I--DID I TELL YOU,
MICHAEL, THAT I RECEIVED

38:00.546 --> 38:06.685
A VERY VERY LUCRATIVE
OFFER FROM COCKS'R'US.NET?

38:06.718 --> 38:10.522
- WHY, NO, EMMETT, YOU DIDN'T.

38:10.556 --> 38:12.891
- DID I TELL YOU,
MICHAEL, ABOUT MY NEW STAR?

38:12.924 --> 38:14.926
DICK LONG.

38:14.960 --> 38:17.896
NOT ONLY LIVES UP TO,
BUT SURPASSES HIS NAME.

38:17.929 --> 38:19.365
- YOU DON'T SAY.

38:19.398 --> 38:21.099
- YOU CAN TELL,
UH, MR. SCHMIDT,

38:21.132 --> 38:23.802
IF YOU HAPPEN TO SEE
HIS WIZENED COUNTENANCE,

38:23.835 --> 38:26.805
THAT HE STILL OWES ME
MY LAST PALTRY PAYCHECK.

38:26.838 --> 38:28.807
- AND, UH, YOU CAN
TELL MR. HONEYCUTT,

38:28.840 --> 38:33.345
WHOSE ASS HAS MORE TREADMARKS
THAN A STEEL-BELTED RADIAL,

38:33.379 --> 38:36.081
IF HE DOESN'T COME BY AND
PICK UP HIS PERSONAL EFFECTS,

38:36.114 --> 38:38.417
HIS DILDOES
WILL BE DONATED TO CHARITY.

38:38.450 --> 38:39.918
- WHY DON'T YOU
TELL EACH OTHER YOURSELVES?

38:39.951 --> 38:41.587
AND WHILE YOU'RE AT IT,
WHY DON'T YOU BOTH APOLOGIZE

38:41.620 --> 38:43.054
FOR ACTING LIKE
A COUPLE OF IDIOTS?

38:43.088 --> 38:44.556
- I'M THE ONE
WHO CREATED HIM.

38:44.590 --> 38:45.824
- YEAH, HE WOULD
BE OUT OF BUSINESS

38:45.857 --> 38:47.359
IF IT WEREN'T FOR ME.

38:47.393 --> 38:48.527
- YOU COULD SHOW
A LITTLE GRATITUDE.

38:48.560 --> 38:49.528
- AND YOU COULD SHOW
A LITTLE GENEROSITY.

38:49.561 --> 38:51.463
- AND YOU BOTH COULD SHOW
A LITTLE MATURITY.

38:51.497 --> 38:52.698
- IT'S NONE OF YOUR
GODDAMNED BUSINESS--

38:52.731 --> 38:53.832
- WHO THE FUCK ASKED
YOUR OPINION ANYWAY?

38:53.865 --> 38:55.834
- JUST BUTT OUT!

39:09.147 --> 39:12.851
- [loud slurping]

39:12.884 --> 39:14.853
MMMM.

39:14.886 --> 39:17.956
[knock on door]

39:31.002 --> 39:33.004
ENJOYING THE VIEW?

39:33.038 --> 39:37.476
- GO AWAY.
- MAKE ME.

39:37.509 --> 39:39.545
YOUR PARTY REALLY SUCKS.

39:39.578 --> 39:41.012
- THAT'S ALREADY
BEEN WELL ESTABLISHED,

39:41.046 --> 39:44.149
IF YOU'VE BEEN
PAYING ATTENTION.

39:48.687 --> 39:52.624
- YOU REALLY GIVE
A SHIT WHAT THEY THINK?

39:52.658 --> 39:55.427
- THEY'RE MY PARENTS, BRIAN.

40:03.669 --> 40:06.071
I KNOW I SHOULDN'T CARE.

40:06.104 --> 40:09.775
I SHOULDN'T
LET IT HURT ME.

40:09.808 --> 40:14.212
IT'S NOT MY JOB
TO PLEASE THEM.

40:14.245 --> 40:17.616
TO MAKE THEM HAPPY.

40:19.818 --> 40:21.853
- YOU REMEMBER...

40:21.887 --> 40:24.490
WHAT'S HIS NAME, UM...

40:24.523 --> 40:27.859
BILLY THE ASSHOLE'S
BIRTHDAY PARTY IN JUNIOR YEAR?

40:30.095 --> 40:32.731
- WHEN REBECCA TUCCI
DUMPED ME?

40:32.764 --> 40:35.567
- THOSE WERE THE DAYS.

40:35.601 --> 40:37.669
- JEEZ, IS THIS SUPPOSED
TO CHEER ME UP?

40:37.703 --> 40:40.539
[chuckles]
I WAS A WRECK.

40:40.572 --> 40:43.008
- NOT FOR LONG.

40:43.041 --> 40:45.644
- THANKS TO YOU
PUTTING "E" IN THE PUNCH,

40:45.677 --> 40:49.815
SOME LOOSE WOMEN
AND THE B-52'S.

40:49.848 --> 40:52.551
- WELL, THOSE WHO DON'T
LEARN THEIR LESSONS

40:52.584 --> 40:55.654
ARE CONDEMNED
TO REPEAT THEIR COURSES.

40:55.687 --> 40:58.657
[muffled rock music playing]

40:58.690 --> 41:04.596
*

