41:37.095 --> 41:38.930
[laughs]

41:38.964 --> 41:41.032
- DOES THAT OFFER STILL STAND?

41:41.066 --> 41:44.035
- * AT THE FLASHBACK, HONEY

41:44.069 --> 41:48.006
* AT THE FLASHBACK, YEAH

41:48.039 --> 41:50.876
