41:50.909 --> 41:53.178
[laughter]

41:53.211 --> 41:55.781
- WHOO!
- [laughs]

41:57.182 --> 41:59.084
MOM.

41:59.117 --> 42:01.587
DADDY.

42:03.188 --> 42:06.057
- YOU CALL THIS BRUNCH?

42:06.091 --> 42:08.827
- HEY. HOW ABOUT SOME PUNCH?
- MEL, NO.

42:10.328 --> 42:13.632
UH, I THOUGHT
YOU WEREN'T COMING.

42:13.665 --> 42:15.867
- WE CHANGED OUR MINDS.

